-1- load modules and install mpi4py

module load 2022r2 slurm
module load openmpi
module load py-mpi4py

#pip install --user mpi4py

There are 4 example scripts to run and check

2019testmpi.slurm
2019hellompi.slurm
2019sendrecv.slurm
2019broadcastmpi.slurm

You can inspect the Python code add change and submit to the queue

sbatch 2019#name.slurm


